description: Support to The National Governance Programme

subproject.description:
Output 1: Capacity of key government institutions further strengthened.
Output 2: Legal frameworks reviewed, revised and validated, and part of the Gambian Consitution translated.
Output 3: Level of awareness on decentralization, local governance and gender issues created among citizens, CSOs and CBOs through sensitization campaigns, meetings and training sessions.
Output 4: National Governance Secretariat and stakeholders further strenghtened through provision of TAs, missions, CTA, etc
